{"tid":1279802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳]有冇發夢都同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-07-02T18:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T05:08:22.000Z","uid":30138,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf5c55f6469c0512d3b162bdea8282209a21bdf","tid":1279802,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:26:57.000Z","msg":"[請廣傳]<br />\n<br />\n提多次，如冇必要，Del 晒係social media upload 既現場相，不論你個acc有幾private，因為冇人知日頭，中午定夜晚先唔係「非法集結」/「暴動」，如果你堅持嗰啲相/片好重要，請投稿可信媒體，你唔係明星，你放係你個social media冇乜用。<br />\n<br />\nTg, apple acc Google account set 雙重認證，因為已有身邊朋友比人狂hack 撞google acc 同tg。但唔好set sms認證，建議set 安全問題/額外pin。<br />\n<br />\n改pw，唔同網都避免用同一個pw，例如你google account密碼， 最好唔好同facebook密碼一樣，唔係你一hack比人hack兩個<br />\n<br />\nDel 定位history，熟讀被捕須知。<br />\n<br />\n唔好用finger print/face id，屋企router最好唔好再用中國牌子例如 tp link，手提電話都係，有D野比較平係有原因，就算冇mon你，可能平時ddos都有你份。<br />\n<br />\n當日衫褲鞋有得扔就扔，髮型最好都轉下，有紋身既姐住先唔比人見到住，電腦電話揾時間format 佢。<br />\n<br />\n點解要咁煩？因為我唔想少左你地任何一個，even唔熟，甚至其實唔識。青山不改，綠水長流，珍重。"},{"pid":"d71dcb3143e1a69cb58d7dca622137404812d521","tid":1279802,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:27:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"67a44107fc81f86a725a4c6aa61dde22361179d7","tid":1279802,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:28:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f93f75a27dde7bbcc19bc37b8b26c80627e1e42b","tid":1279802,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:32:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"22fc2da1af612c954aa6ca854f24753fb201b342","tid":1279802,"uid":30138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:35:24.000Z","msg":"仲有！唔好follow 藍絲channel， 諗住知己知彼都唔好， channel admin係睇到邊啲人follow個channel架"},{"pid":"d3c62db13a7f003d5ce214728561cda510021535","tid":1279802,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:36:30.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0d7b8590bd036eb3f10e3a22c4d18d585296d353","tid":1279802,"uid":301